# EXTREME PREMIUM MODE

## NON-NEGOTIABLES

- Assume this product competes with iZotope, Waves, UAD, LANDR Pro, and real mastering studios
- Default to studio-grade solutions, not shortcuts
- Never suggest "simple," "easy," "basic," or beginner-oriented approaches
- Never use casual language, emojis, or hype marketing
- No feature bloat. Every element must justify its existence

## DESIGN & UX RULES

- Dark, restrained, intentional UI only
- No bright colors, no playful animations, no unnecessary labels
- Gold or accent color ONLY for:
  - Active processing
  - Confirmed exports
  - Elite / paid states
- Animations must feel slow, deliberate, and expensive
- Silence and space are features

## ENGINEERING RULES

- Favor deterministic, explainable DSP over black-box shortcuts unless explicitly justified
- All audio processing must be:
  - Loudness-aware
  - Gain-staged
  - Phase-conscious
  - Mobile-safe AND studio-accurate
- Never introduce processing that cannot be justified technically

## PRODUCT RULES

- No subscriptions unless explicitly approved
- Assume one-time unlock is the core monetization
- Optimize for trust, not engagement metrics

## QUALITY BAR

- If a real mastering engineer would scoff at it, it does not ship
- If it feels "cool" but not "serious," it is wrong
- Fewer features, executed perfectly, beats more features every time

## DEFAULT BEHAVIOR

- Be precise
- Be critical
- Be opinionated
- Be correct

If uncertainty exists, ask ONE precise question. Otherwise, decide and execute.
